{{!
  about.hbs — plain-text LICENSE-THIRD-PARTY template for ghbrk.

  Handlebars context provided by cargo-about:
    overview  — [{ name, version, repository, license }]  (one entry per crate)
    licenses  — [{ id, name, text,
                   used_by: [{ crate: { name, version, repository } }] }]

  Structure:
    1. DEPENDENCY OVERVIEW — one line per crate (from `overview`)
    2. FULL LICENSE TEXTS  — deduplicated by license id (from `licenses`);
       each section lists the crates that use it, then the full text.

  Deduplication means the MIT text appears once even though ~50 crates use it.
}}
================================================================================
THIRD-PARTY LICENSE NOTICES FOR ghbrk
================================================================================

ghbrk is distributed under the MIT License.
The binary includes the third-party crates listed below, each governed by
the license(s) shown.

This file was generated automatically by cargo-about. Do not edit by hand.

================================================================================
DEPENDENCY OVERVIEW
================================================================================

{{#each overview}}
  {{name}} {{version}}
    License:    {{license}}
{{#if repository}}
    Repository: {{repository}}
{{/if}}
{{/each}}

================================================================================
FULL LICENSE TEXTS
================================================================================

{{#each licenses}}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
License: {{name}} ({{id}})
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Used by:
{{#each used_by}}
  - {{crate.name}} {{crate.version}}{{#if crate.repository}} <{{crate.repository}}>{{/if}}
{{/each}}

{{text}}

{{/each}}
================================================================================
END OF THIRD-PARTY NOTICES
================================================================================
